  "description": "<p>\n\t&nbsp;<img src=\"http://n1image.hjfile.cn/mh/2016/12/09/53f97ff5dbb189f316cde7ca77dac30c.jpg\" /></p>\n<p>\n\tWe usually need to have a self introduction in the first part of our resume, and the most important part may be your working experiences. &nbsp;The interviewer&rsquo;s decision will be mainly depend on your working experiences. If you have the related or the same experiences, you need to hand over your working experiences fully and correctly. Here is an example of experiences as a volunteer:</p>\n<p>\n\t&ldquo;From August 2014 to July 2015, I worked as a volunteer in the local government of Qiaoqi Tibetan township, mainly responsible for the clerical works and dealing with the disputes among natives and also broadcasting the related policies. Then from September 2015 till now I worked in the Tourism Bureau of Ya&rsquo;an City. My duty is to advertising the tourist sites of the city. In August 2015, 9 panda fans from Europe visited Sichuan and during their stay in Ya&rsquo;an, we the workers together introduced the history of discovery of panda and visited the artificial panda breeding base. In the following month I worked as a translator and participated in the 2<sup>nd</sup> Sichuan International Travel Expo, introduced the tourism of the Ya&rsquo;an city, including local specialties and tea culture and most importantly the panda, to the potential investors from over 20 countries. In July 2016, once again, I worked as a translator during the banquet, provide the 100 travel agency managers from around the country and the world the information of Ya&rsquo;an tourism, and unforgettably received the praise from the audiences.&rdquo; &nbsp;&nbsp;</p>\n<p>\n\t现在小编来给大家解析一下这篇介绍这片工作经验范文。作者通过时间顺序介绍了自己作为乡镇政府办公室职员的工作和在市区旅游部门的工作，以及作为一个翻译者的经历。说出了具体的时间和事件，给人以充分详实的印象。歪果仁注重实际效用和诚实严谨的态度，所以不能瞎编乱造自己的工作经历和能力，不然一旦被发现，必然不利于工作的进一步展开。记住，真诚在任何时候都不会是错。Never forget that sincerity will never be blamed.</p>\n<br /><center><a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/new/p959903/#relate_articles\"><img src=\"http://en.hujiang.com/2009/images/rss_chat.jpg\" style=\"border: 0;\" /></a> <a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/new/p959903\"><img src=\"http://en.hujiang.com/2009/images/rss_digg.jpg\" style=\"border: 0;\" /></a></center><h3 style=\"margin: 10px;\">本周最热文章</h3><ul style=\"margin: 5px 0;\"><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p957793/\">国家地理2016年度最佳摄影作品：感动！震撼！</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p955925/\">四级阅读：信息匹配题做题小技巧</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p776149/\">2016年英语六级作文模板大集合（持续更新）</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p955801/\">内向的人来看~ 教你10句大招，用过都说好~</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p776141/\">2016年英语四级作文模板集锦（持续更新）</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p955937/\">另类世界地图：各国都包揽了哪些世界第一？</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p957784/\">（高频词汇）limitation＆limiting＆limitless用法综述</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p955747/\">Quora精选：妈妈给过你的最好忠告是什么？</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p943796/\">四六级翻译写作必备之黄金过渡词</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p955880/\">学会这些表达，让你的口语更地道</a></li></ul><div style=\"margin-top: 10px;\">导航:  <a href=\"http://www.hujiang.com/\" style=\"margin: 5px;\" target=\"_black\">沪江网</a>  <a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/\" style=\"margin: 5px;\" target=\"_black\">沪江英语</a>  <a href=\"http://jp.hujiang.com/\" style=\"margin: 5px;\" target=\"_black\">沪江日语</a>  <a href=\"http://fr.hujiang.com/\" style=\"margin: 5px;\" target=\"_black\">沪江法语</a>  <a href=\"http://kr.hujiang.com\" style=\"margin: 5px;\" target=\"_black\">沪江韩语</a></div><hr style=\"border: 0.5px solid gray;\" 